title: R.E.M. - Monster [1994][Ogg Vorbis Q8]
description:
R.E.M. - Monster [1994][Ogg Vorbis Q8]

Monster is R.E.M.&#039;s ninth album, and their fourth major label release for Warner Bros., released in 1994. It is their most guitar-heavy album to date, with glam/70s rock and grunge influences. It is also very multi-layered, with references to projected images, both in the media and in personal identity, particularly in terms of sexuality.

All songs written by Bill Berry, Peter Buck, Mike Mills and Michael Stipe.
